Package: ceR
Title: A R package for Illumina BaseSpace Correlation Engine (CE) API 
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Zhang (Frank)", "Cheng", , "fcheng@illumina.com", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0003-3863-2866"))
Description: BaseSpace Correlation Engine mines over 23,000 (and growing) scientific studies to get data-driven answers for genes, experiments, drugs and phenotypes for your research. This pacakge wrapped all CE API to facilitate data mining and machine learning using CE's database in R.
